    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Beginning at 3rd level, choose between Taijutsu, Genjutsu, or Ninjutsu. You reduce the downtime needed to learn jutsu and feats of that type by 2 weeks. This increases to 4 weeks at 7th level and to 6 weeks at 11th level.</p><p>Additionally, twice per rest when making a skill check you are proficient in, you can treat a d20 roll of 9 or lower as a 10.</p>",
